room_title: Escape room "Rendyth's Revenge" by Kingdom Escape Games in Key Largo
room_description: King Blamsfar is in possession of Rendyths three Eggs and has total control over this peaceful Dragon. He is using this power to take over one realm at a time, and yours is next! It is up to you and your crusaders to infiltrate the castle, steal back Rendyth's eggs, and give her power back so she can take revenge upon the evil King.
